Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:59.80,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Por isso, por favor, garanta meu desejo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:02.40,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(Eu tenho apenas um)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:07.62,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A primavera que você procura aqui
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:09.92,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ainda não acabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:14.72,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eu nunca poderei alcançar a eternidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:17.30,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(Eu nem sei o caminho de volta para casa)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.89,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eu não posso voltar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:24.73,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}O caminho atrás de mim começa a desaparecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:29.23,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Guiando os dois que estão para se conhecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:33.61,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Se este momento for o início de tudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:37.57,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Na mansão proibida,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.99,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}eu vou mostrar que posso amar tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:44.91,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Por isso, se o que me espera é uma armadilha,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.50,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}eu vou apenas rir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:52.38,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mesmos as minhas memórias de tristeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:56.08,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eu vou usar ferramentas para te torturar,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:59.09,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}e sussurrar apenas uma coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:03.22,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dis Code
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:06.77,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A incessante chuva leva você com ela,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.65,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}para o paraíso final,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:16.00,Translation,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}onde tudo começa...
